{"tid":1398944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我今次唔攬炒]「集會前夕」和理非可以點樣係重大戰役幫前線？以後一齊接放學啦！！","createTime":"2019-08-03T03:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T12:54:53.000Z","uid":89974,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"18d51d522cf49eae67e078814be5ad99df2b09e3","tid":1398944,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前言：</span></span><br />\n次次大會見到前線亡命抵抗，你想除咗食花生涼冷氣之外都出一分力？見到好多家長有車接仔女放學，好想幫手救人？<br />\n三十歲人都仲要依賴交通工具嘅你地都得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家一齊落去地鐵站食花生！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目標：</span></span><br />\n保障每一個放學仔女既安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n增加士氣，話俾前線聽好多人撐佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行動綱領：</span></span><br />\n如果你有發開夢，當日係附近奧運，旺角，油麻地地鐵站：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁早撤退！11點前都留係站內做支援！你一個普通人食完飯途經地鐵站係唔會俾人拉架！<br />\n唔好咁早撤退！11點前都留係站內做支援！你一個普通人食完飯途經地鐵站係唔會俾人拉架！<br />\n唔好咁早撤退！11點前都留係站內做支援！你一個普通人食完飯途經地鐵站係唔會俾人拉架！<br />\n<br />\n如果你個日要番屋企食飯，落唔到場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每逢有大型活動，夜晚9-12點落去最近你屋企嘅地鐵站涼冷氣散步睇直播<strong>放下狗</strong><br />\n每逢有大型活動，夜晚9-12點落去最近你屋企嘅地鐵站涼冷氣散步睇直播<em>放下狗</em><br />\n每逢有大型活動，夜晚9-12點落去最近你屋企嘅地鐵站涼冷氣散步睇直播<strong>放下狗</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Q&amp;A</span></span><br />\n1. 接放學著乜好？<br />\n街坊裝又得，黑色衫又得，香港地好易病記住帶口罩，夏天成日打風攞定直遮<br />\n<br />\n2. 要查我身份證喎，點算？<br />\n問佢攞委任證先，記住你人愈多愈安全，班狗係唔會兇你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重複多幾次：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔駛早撤退！多落街跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔駛早撤退！多落街跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔駛早撤退！多落街跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n我會每次集會前將會重開一次呢個POST提醒大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f33959c19d8a8e77e864152e364aba71fc1101","tid":1398944,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22073be5bf5d1cc037e089e8ec46d9d98cfc2739","tid":1398944,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:01:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e42f34e6ebeee7ba9ddd73951389665a4c34ab1","tid":1398944,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62b7af4ae6408eb83d1fc28b81fe0089ed14439","tid":1398944,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a072e319826e3cd31e3904866be1516cbc2bb9f9","tid":1398944,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccd5efd0c3997b31707cd08259ab5b3e792437a","tid":1398944,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj